<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='619000' id='t-619000'>Compare them to the tools our ancestors used;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='622000' id='t-622000'>they bear a striking resemblance to Kanzi's.</span>
