</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
15:52
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='941000' id='t-941000'>Researcher: OK, now get the monsters. Get them.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='944000' id='t-944000'>Take the cherries too.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='947000' id='t-947000'>Now watch out, stay away from them now.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='951000' id='t-951000'>Now you can chase them again. Time to chase them.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='958000' id='t-958000'>Now you have to stay away. Get away.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='961000' id='t-961000'>Run away. Run.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='964000' id='t-964000'>Now we can chase them again. Go get them.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='970000' id='t-970000'>Oh no!</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='972000' id='t-972000'>Good Kanzi. Very good. Thank you so much.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
16:30
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='979000' id='t-979000'>Narrator: None of us, Bonobo or human, can possibly even imagine?</span>
